description.short: Rectangular flags in natural colours with outlines.
description.full:
The alphabet (A-Z) flags are rectangular with a 4x3 aspect ratio.

All images have outlines so they are suitable for display or
printing on a white background.

Colours have been selected to appear similar to real flags and pennants in
common use.
